The Mask;;68;;79;;PG-13;;When timid bank clerk Stanley Ipkiss (Jim Carrey) discovers a magical mask containing the spirit of the Norse god Loki, his entire life changes. While wearing the mask, Ipkiss becomes a supernatural playboy exuding charm and confidence which allows him to catch the eye of local nightclub singer Tina Carlyle (Cameron Diaz). Unfortunately, under the mask's influence, Ipkiss also robs a bank, which angers junior crime lord Dorian Tyrell (Peter Greene), whose goons get blamed for the heist.;;Comedy;;Chuck Russell;;1994;;Jim Carrey,Cameron Diaz,Peter Riegert,Peter Greene,Amy Yasbeck,Richard Jeni,Orestes Matacena,Tim Bagley,Nancy Fish,Johnny Williams;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1053779-mask